                  var pa = PlatformAnalytics.getInstance();
                  pa.markPageUsable();
                });
              } else {
                 ewe_performance.markPageUsable();
              }
              if (console &amp;&amp; typeof console.timeStamp === 'function') {
                  console.timeStamp('mark page usable');
              }
          }

          function determineMarkPageUsableStrategy() {
            if(window.requestAnimationFrame &amp;&amp; typeof window.requestAnimationFrame === 'function') {
              window.requestAnimationFrame(markPageUsable);
            } else {
              markPageUsable();
            }
          }

          if(window.mercuryFormsInitialized === true) {
            determineMarkPageUsableStrategy();
          } else {
              uitk.subscribe('mercuryForms.initialized', function(topic, obj) {
                determineMarkPageUsableStrategy();
                uitk.unsubscribe('mercuryForms.initialized');
              });
          }
        })
    </script>

              <form id="gcw-flights-form-hp-flight" class="gcw-form flights gcw-prepopulate-flying-from gcw-grey-out-irrelevant-dates flexible-shopping-form gcw-traveler-selector gcw-oneway-packages gcw-lessThanNTravelers-travelerSelector gcw-unattendedInfantInLap-travelerSelector gcw-childAgesAllProvided-travelerSelector gcw-allFlightsComplete gcw-allOriginsAreDifferentFromDestinations gcw-dynamic-leg-fields field-border-in-high-contrast-mode ess-passthrough-disabled" data-gcw-key="hp-flight" data-gcw-max-travelers="6" action="/Flights-Search" method="GET" data-gcw-processing-function="flights" data-gcw-datapreloading-function="flights" data-gcw-controller="flights" data-locale="en_US" data-siteid="1" data-location-search-type="uta" data-lob-form="flight" data-gcw-current-package-type="flight">
  <div class="mobile-hero-banner-title">

<script type="text/javascript">
    require(['gc/pageModel', 'jquery', 'dctk/dctk'], function (pageModel, $, dctk) {
        var user = pageModel.user;
        var site = pageModel.site;
        var modE2EWhiteRecognisedNonUSExpId = 24998;
        var modE2EWhiteRecognisedUSExpId = 16349;
        var userType = (user) ? user.userStatus : undefined;
        var el = $('.member-pricing-wizard-message');
        if (userType === 'Identified' || userType === 'AUTHENTICATED') {
          if (window.modRebrandingExperimentEnabledNonUS) {
            evaluateExperiment(modE2EWhiteRecognisedNonUSExpId);
               } else if (window.memberOnlyDealsEnabled) {
               if (!window.modOptimisedE2eIdentifiedExpEnabled) {
               evaluateExperiment(modE2EWhiteRecognisedUSExpId);
               }
             }
            else {
             el.show();
           }
        }

        function evaluateExperiment(experimentId) {
            dctk.evaluateExperimentAndLog({
                id: experimentId,
                guid: pageModel.user.guid,
                tpid: pageModel.site.tpid,
                eapid: pageModel.site.eapid,
                callback: function (experiment) {
                    if (experiment.value === 0) {
                        el.show();
                    }
                }
            });
        }

    })
</script>

            function ABTest(childId, validToLog, useControl, controlValues) {
                this.child = childId;
                this.validToLog = validToLog;
                this.value = parseInt(window.serverABTests['ab' + this.child], 10);
                if(isNaN(this.value)){
                    this.value = -1;
                }
                this.useControlMarquee = useControl === true &amp;&amp; ( controlValues.length === 0 || controlValues.indexOf(this.value) &gt;= 0 );
                this.cmptst = this.child + '.' + this.value;
            }
            var tests = [];
            var marqueeVNextChildId = 24784;
            var marqueeVNextParentId = 24783;
            var imageHostingChildId = 27689;
            var imageHostingThrottledOn = (serverABTests['ab27688'/* parent experiment */] === 1);
            /* add parent child tests below: */
            tests.push(new ABTest(window.mesoNativeMarqueeChildId, window.mesoNativeMarqueeValidToLog, true, [0]));
            tests.push(new ABTest(marqueeVNextChildId, (serverABTests['ab' + marqueeVNextParentId] === 1), true, [0,1]));
            tests.push(new ABTest(imageHostingChildId, imageHostingThrottledOn, true, [0]));

            marqueeAdConfig.updatedTargeting = marqueeAdConfig.updatedTargeting || {};
            var CMPTSTs = [];
            if (marqueeAdConfig.updatedTargeting.CMPTST) {
                CMPTSTs.push(marqueeAdConfig.updatedTargeting.CMPTST);
            }
            for (var t in tests) {
                if (tests[t].validToLog === true &amp;&amp; CMPTSTs.indexOf(tests[t].cmptst) &lt; 0) {
                    CMPTSTs.push(tests[t].cmptst);
                    /* TODO: Remove below if-block after AbTests have run */
                    if (tests[t].useControlMarquee &amp;&amp; marqueeAdConfig.adCalls &amp;&amp; marqueeAdConfig.adCalls[marqueeAdConfig.adToLoad]) {
                        var OLDPATH = 'MARQUEE';
                        var NEWPATH = 'MARQUEECONTROL';
                        var adPage = marqueeAdConfig.adToLoad;
                        var url = marqueeAdConfig.adCalls[adPage].url;
                        var path = marqueeAdConfig.adCalls[adPage].path;
                        if (url) {
                            marqueeAdConfig.adCalls[adPage].url = url.replace(OLDPATH, NEWPATH);
                        }
                        if (path) {
                            marqueeAdConfig.adCalls[adPage].path = path.replace(OLDPATH, NEWPATH);
                        }
                    }
                    /* END TEST CODE */
                }
            }
            if (CMPTSTs.length &gt; 0) {
                marqueeAdConfig.updatedTargeting.CMPTST = CMPTSTs.join(',');
            }
            //Post the resource timings for the marquee image
            if (imageHostingThrottledOn &amp;&amp; expads.analytics &amp;&amp; expads.analytics.postPerformanceEntry &amp;&amp; expads.events
              &amp;&amp; expads.events.postMarqueeImageLoaded &amp;&amp; expads.events.postMarqueeImageLoaded.attachHandler) {
                expads.events.postMarqueeImageLoaded.attachHandler(function (x) {
                    if (x.selector === "#hero-banner") {
                        expads.analytics.postPerformanceEntry(x.url);
                    }
                });
            }
            return marqueeAdConfig;
        } catch (e) {
          window.logError('sfError', e, { notes: 'marquee/setCMPTST' });
        }
    });
</script>

        display: none;
    }
</style>

                if (dctk &amp;&amp; dctk.ewePerformance &amp;&amp; (typeof dctk.ewePerformance.addData === 'function')) {
                    for (var experimentId in perfTracking) {
                        if (perfTracking.hasOwnProperty(experimentId)) {
                            var bucket = perfTracking[experimentId];
                            if (experimentId &amp;&amp; typeof bucket === 'number') {
                                dctk.ewePerformance.addData(experimentId, bucket.toString());
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            });
        }
        if (perfTracking) {
            trackExperiments(perfTracking);
        }

    })();
</script>
